            <div type="section" xml:id="Legislation">
                <head>Legislation</head>
                <p> Archives are subject to different time periods of declassification, with some
                    records made available after 25 years and others after 50 years. </p>
            </div>
            <div type="section" xml:id="Location">
                <head>Location</head>
                <p>National Archives, B.P. 1053, Yaoundé.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="section" xml:id="Procedures">
                <head> Procedures</head>
                <p>Researchers are advised to write the National Archives and the Ministry of
                    Foreign Affairs to inquire as to the availability of diplomatic records.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="section" xml:id="Website">
                <head>Website</head>
                <p>
                    <ref target="http://www.spm.gov.cm/">Government of Cameroon and Ministry of
                        Foreign Affairs</ref>
                </p>
